The paper discusses the optimization of convolutional neural networks (CNN) using a metaheuristic algorithm, specifically the linearly decreasing weight particle swarm optimization (LDWPSO). This falls under the category of neural networks (cs.NE) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of CNNs also relates to computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the optimization technique used can be applied to control systems (cs.SY).
